text: Joseph Caley is a British ballet dancer, and a lead principal with the English National Ballet. Caley was born in Hull, England.https://www.ballet.org.uk/people/joseph- caley/https://www.ballet.org.uk/blog-detail/joseph-caley-promoted-lead- principal/ He trained at the Royal Ballet School.https://www.ballet.org.uk/blog-detail/joseph-caley-joins-new- principal-2017-18-season/ Caley joined the Birmingham Royal Ballet in 2005, and became a principal in 2011. He joined English National Ballet in 2017, and was promoted to lead principal in December. ==References== Category:British male ballet dancers Category:Living people Category:Birmingham Royal Ballet principal dancers Category:People educated at the Royal Ballet School Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
